params.markdown:
#### Island Browser

#### Overview

This dashboard provides visibility into admin action events across the Island Browser platform and supports analysts in security monitoring.

Filters let you refine results by tenant and entity name. Time-series charts show admin action events over time, and bar and pie charts break down events by action type, action status, and action domain. Tables showcase the top source IPs from which actions were performed.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/island_browser/overview)**
